query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `purchase_order_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchaseOrderId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sparePartId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `unitPrice` decimal(12,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `totalPrice` decimal(12,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receivedQuantity` int(11) DEFAULT 0,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_po_items_purchaseOrderId` (`purchaseOrderId`),
  KEY `idx_po_items_sparePartId` (`sparePartId`)
);
